name: ApacheTrashDay
0:
”Alexa, ask Trash day when is the next trash day”
”Alexa, ask Trash day when is the next recycle pickup”
”Alexa, ask Trash day when is the next trash pickup”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: trash day
des: TrashDay uses the TDS calendar (example here: http://www.texasdisposal.com/sites/default/files/uploads/TDS_ResidentialServiceCalendar-2016.pdf) to figure out when your next trash or recycle day is.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
